languages.text: "Взгляни на этот след. Кого-то протащили... нет, кто-то прошел нам навстречу, совсем недавно. Но мы никого не видели..."
"Look at this mark. Someone was dragged... no, someone walked in our direction very recently. But we didn't see anyone..."

languages.text: «Observe estas marcas. Han arrastrado... no, alguien ha caminado en nuestra dirección hace muy poco. Y sin embargo no hemos visto a nadie...».
languages.original_text: "Look at this mark. Someone was dragged... no, someone walked in our direction very recently. But we didn't see anyone..."

traits.locale_text: «Observe estas marcas. Han arrastrado... no, alguien ha caminado en nuestra dirección hace muy poco. Y sin embargo no hemos visto a nadie...».

languages.text: 「この痕跡を見ろ。誰かが引きずられた…いや、ごく最近、誰かがこっちの方に歩いてきたようだ。だが、我々は誰の姿も見ていない…」
languages.original_text: "Look at this mark. Someone was dragged... no, someone walked in our direction very recently. But we didn't see anyone..."

traits.locale_text: 「この痕跡を見ろ。誰かが引きずられた…いや、ごく最近、誰かがこっちの方に歩いてきたようだ。だが、我々は誰の姿も見ていない…」

languages.text: "Seht Euch diese Spur an. Jemand wurde geschleift ... nein, jemand ist vor Kurzem in unsere Richtung gegangen. Aber wir haben niemanden gesehen ..."
languages.original_text: "Look at this mark. Someone was dragged... no, someone walked in our direction very recently. But we didn't see anyone..."

languages.text: « Regardez cette marque. Quelqu'un a été tiré... Non, quelqu'un a marché dans notre direction très récemment. Pourtant, nous n'avons vu personne... »

languages.text: "Şu ize baksana. Birini sürüklemişler... Yok, birisi gittiğimiz yöne doğru yürümüş, daha demin hem de. Gerçi kimseyi görmedik..."
